WEBVTT

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:24.500
"Love After Addiction"

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:26.600
(Episode 12)

00:01:49.359 --> 00:01:51.120
Please have a seat and rest here.

00:01:56.599 --> 00:01:57.599
Not bad.

00:01:58.519 --> 00:01:59.599
Sis, the style here is

00:01:59.760 --> 00:02:00.760
pretty minimalist.

00:02:00.959 --> 00:02:02.599
And the theme is quite rustic.

00:02:03.319 --> 00:02:04.359
Better than I imagined.

00:02:07.519 --> 00:02:09.080
Ranran, I am tired.

00:02:10.199 --> 00:02:11.400
Sis, you guys rest first.

00:02:11.560 --> 00:02:13.240
I'll ask the restaurant to prepare dinner.

00:02:13.360 --> 00:02:14.536
Your luggage will be brought over soon.

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:15.560
Can I tag along with you?

00:02:17.319 --> 00:02:19.039
Sis, take a rest first.

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:21.800
Let's go.

00:02:25.618 --> 00:02:26.960
Give me your phone number.

00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:35.759
Hello.

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:36.520
Hello.

00:02:36.639 --> 00:02:37.816
Could you please check us into a room?

00:02:37.840 --> 00:02:38.840
Sure, one moment please.

00:02:42.879 --> 00:02:44.295
Now we only have one twin room left.

00:02:44.319 --> 00:02:46.159
But it's not an ocean
view room. Is that okay?

00:02:46.199 --> 00:02:47.199
We want a king-size bed.

00:02:52.520 --> 00:02:53.960
Two men sleeping in a king-size bed.

00:02:56.960 --> 00:02:57.960
Done?

00:02:58.639 --> 00:02:59.639
Sure thing!

00:02:59.919 --> 00:03:01.319
The poached shrimp is almost ready.

00:03:01.439 --> 00:03:02.439
Okay.

00:03:04.479 --> 00:03:05.999
The shrimp is ready, you can serve it.

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:12.000
Is the garlic ready?

00:03:12.120 --> 00:03:13.120
Come on, come on.

00:04:08.120 --> 00:04:09.120
Head north.

00:04:10.520 --> 00:04:11.240
Still need about

00:04:11.360 --> 00:04:12.520
three more days to get out.

00:04:20.600 --> 00:04:21.600
Any more?

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:24.319
There is.

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:25.560
Here.

00:04:32.120 --> 00:04:34.040
Three little chickens and a hippo.

00:04:34.120 --> 00:04:35.120
Sitting in a row.

00:04:35.360 --> 00:04:35.959
The chicken

00:04:36.079 --> 00:04:37.159
sitting on the fourth board

00:04:37.199 --> 00:04:38.279
said to the hippo

00:04:38.439 --> 00:04:39.439
on the third board:

00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:41.240
Let's switch places.

00:04:41.680 --> 00:04:43.040
The hippo asked, "Why?"

00:04:43.879 --> 00:04:44.879
The chicken said:

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:46.120
You'll know once you switch.

00:04:46.439 --> 00:04:47.560
So...

00:04:48.399 --> 00:04:49.399
So...

00:04:50.199 --> 00:04:51.199
the chair collapsed.

00:04:53.360 --> 00:04:54.480
Let me think about it again.

00:04:55.832 --> 00:04:56.832
Can't figure it out.

00:04:57.000 --> 00:04:58.000
Son, tell me quickly.

00:04:59.079 --> 00:05:00.079
As a result...

00:05:00.600 --> 00:05:02.000
the chicken disappeared.

00:05:02.519 --> 00:05:03.519
Why?

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:07.507
Happy Match. [TN: He's making a joke about
the name of a a match-3 game but with animals]

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:13.720
This...

00:05:16.439 --> 00:05:17.040
Dad, I'm done eating.

00:05:17.439 --> 00:05:18.439
I'll go wash the dishes.

00:05:19.360 --> 00:05:20.360
No, no, no need.

00:05:20.399 --> 00:05:21.040
I'll clean up.

00:05:21.319 --> 00:05:22.319
You should rest early.

00:05:25.360 --> 00:05:26.360
Get to bed early, yeah?

00:05:50.433 --> 00:05:51.873
(From: Wyndham Hui-Hui)

00:05:51.920 --> 00:05:54.000
I bought two circus tickets.

00:05:54.759 --> 00:05:55.855
But my friend suddenly has something to do.

00:05:55.879 --> 00:05:56.879
So he can't make it.

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:07.399
Do you have time?

00:06:08.120 --> 00:06:09.120
No.

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:17.560
Sure.

00:06:42.040 --> 00:06:43.040
Sorry.

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:45.920
I thought you were Korean.

00:06:48.759 --> 00:06:49.759
What's your name?

00:06:50.720 --> 00:06:51.720
Yoki.

00:06:52.199 --> 00:06:53.199
Yoki.

00:06:53.639 --> 00:06:54.680
Thank you, Yoki.

00:06:55.519 --> 00:06:56.560
If without you,

00:06:57.360 --> 00:06:59.720
I would not be able to bring anything

00:07:00.079 --> 00:07:02.560
and go see the God in early.

00:07:05.800 --> 00:07:07.879
You, rest here.

00:07:19.920 --> 00:07:20.920
Thank you.

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:25.240
Good night.

00:07:25.319 --> 00:07:26.319
Good night.

00:07:52.680 --> 00:07:53.680
Feels like

00:07:54.040 --> 00:07:56.081
you don't miss me as
much as you said you did.

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:58.519
Isn't that because...

00:07:58.680 --> 00:07:59.680
Because of what?

00:08:02.279 --> 00:08:03.279
Because of my sister?

00:08:03.959 --> 00:08:05.360
Then you can't control your time.

00:08:07.120 --> 00:08:08.120
Next time, can you

00:08:08.199 --> 00:08:09.279
not look at me like that?

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:12.720
Every time I see that
expression on your face,

00:08:13.920 --> 00:08:15.240
I can't control myself.

00:08:16.720 --> 00:08:18.040
Then what expression do you want?

00:08:25.000 --> 00:08:25.600
Mr. Xu.

00:08:25.720 --> 00:08:26.976
The two male guests who
checked in during the day

00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:28.160
want to have a word with you.

00:08:29.519 --> 00:08:30.600
Alright, I got it.

00:08:50.240 --> 00:08:51.240
Sis,

00:08:51.960 --> 00:08:52.960
you were looking for me?

00:08:58.480 --> 00:08:58.799
Sis,

00:08:58.800 --> 00:09:00.278
all the houses you can see

00:09:00.279 --> 00:09:01.279
are all mine.

00:09:01.399 --> 00:09:02.416
The entire island's homestays

00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:03.440
also belong to me.

00:09:03.919 --> 00:09:04.919
Really?

00:09:05.559 --> 00:09:07.399
Have you heard of the Xu Guang Group?

00:09:08.080 --> 00:09:09.080
Xu Guang?

00:09:09.919 --> 00:09:10.919
Xu Guanghan?

00:09:11.679 --> 00:09:12.679
That's my dad.

00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:14.480
The son of the Xu Guang Group.

00:09:14.639 --> 00:09:15.799
Isn't he called Xu Qing?

00:09:16.145 --> 00:09:17.159
That's my older brother.

00:09:19.440 --> 00:09:20.440
Really?

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:22.079
Sis, if you don't believe me,

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:23.319
I can have my father

00:09:23.320 --> 00:09:24.320
call you right now.

00:09:24.759 --> 00:09:26.120
Does Ranran know about this?

00:09:29.360 --> 00:09:30.360
Why didn't you tell him?

00:09:31.200 --> 00:09:32.200
What are you afraid of?

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:34.440
Afraid we'll cling to you?

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:37.080
I...

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:41.039
Sis, I'm sorry.

00:09:41.399 --> 00:09:43.240
I'm really not how you think I am.

00:09:44.200 --> 00:09:45.600
You know what I think?

00:09:46.080 --> 00:09:47.999
Aren't you just trying to give me money

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:49.000
to make me leave him?

00:09:50.320 --> 00:09:51.679
This is your dating fund.

00:09:55.399 --> 00:09:56.320
It really is just like

00:09:56.321 --> 00:09:57.639
what Ranran said.

00:10:02.080 --> 00:10:02.799
Thank you.

00:10:02.800 --> 00:10:04.840
For bringing me back to your country.

00:10:05.200 --> 00:10:06.320
I really like here.

00:10:07.000 --> 00:10:08.000
As you said:

00:10:08.360 --> 00:10:09.839
Even if you accompany a
horse for a thousand miles

00:10:09.840 --> 00:10:11.320
there must be a parting.

00:10:12.600 --> 00:10:13.600
No, no, no.

00:10:13.759 --> 00:10:16.080
It's "Even if you accompany a gentleman for
a thousand miles, there must be a parting."

00:10:18.480 --> 00:10:20.600
You'll for sure see each other.

00:10:20.960 --> 00:10:21.960
Believe me.

00:10:23.279 --> 00:10:25.799
The Earth is round.

00:10:28.360 --> 00:10:29.360
Bye, oh Lei. [TN: They're setting up a really
bad pun here that doesn't work in any language]

00:10:30.720 --> 00:10:31.720
Only?

00:10:32.519 --> 00:10:33.519
No, no, no.

00:10:34.039 --> 00:10:35.039
Only.

00:10:35.240 --> 00:10:37.759
That person is your only one.

00:10:42.720 --> 00:10:43.720
Thank you.

00:10:48.519 --> 00:10:49.519
You...

00:10:49.720 --> 00:10:52.080
give me your email contact please.

00:10:52.440 --> 00:10:52.919
Okay.

00:10:53.159 --> 00:10:54.200
Bye, see you.

00:11:11.802 --> 00:11:13.376
(Ye Ran: Yoki bro, text me
when you see this, it's urgent)

00:11:29.039 --> 00:11:30.039
Brother Yoki.

00:11:30.320 --> 00:11:31.080
At Che's homestay,

00:11:31.080 --> 00:11:32.080
two men came.

00:11:32.360 --> 00:11:35.000
They said they're your and Yang
Meng's middle school classmates.

00:11:36.120 --> 00:11:36.639
It seems

00:11:36.840 --> 00:11:38.240
they've spent all their money here.

00:11:39.080 --> 00:11:41.495
They've taken a liking to the
Che's café at the top of the mountain.

00:11:41.519 --> 00:11:42.999
They want to hold their wedding here.

00:11:43.480 --> 00:11:44.880
The time is the day after tomorrow.

00:11:45.080 --> 00:11:46.080
Will you come back?

00:11:47.279 --> 00:11:48.279
You...

00:11:48.360 --> 00:11:50.000
I'm ready to boarding now,

00:11:50.320 --> 00:11:51.479
and I look forward to

00:11:51.480 --> 00:11:53.440
eat a pie my wife makes,

00:11:53.840 --> 00:11:56.158
and drink the tea I love

00:11:56.159 --> 00:11:57.200
from my father.

00:11:57.320 --> 00:11:58.320
On my way,

00:11:58.399 --> 00:12:00.279
I've been thinking of your experience,

00:12:00.639 --> 00:12:01.840
I'm deeply moved.

00:12:02.120 --> 00:12:02.679
This is

00:12:02.680 --> 00:12:04.440
an irrepressible story.

00:12:04.600 --> 00:12:07.000
I want to develop it into a film.

00:12:07.279 --> 00:12:09.879
And I want to ask you for your permission.

00:12:10.399 --> 00:12:11.080
Besides,

00:12:11.279 --> 00:12:12.398
I want you to fly

00:12:12.399 --> 00:12:14.239
to New York, the day after.

00:12:14.240 --> 00:12:15.399
And meet my producer.

00:12:15.960 --> 00:12:16.960
I didn't tell you,

00:12:17.080 --> 00:12:18.799
but I'm a director.

00:12:19.000 --> 00:12:20.720
Looking forward to your response.

00:12:22.759 --> 00:12:24.360
Can we let each other go?

00:12:26.159 --> 00:12:27.279
You let me go.

00:12:53.279 --> 00:12:54.279
The day after tomorrow,

00:12:54.759 --> 00:12:55.279
I also want to try

00:12:55.440 --> 00:12:56.440
the pie your wife makes.

00:13:08.240 --> 00:13:09.240
Can't go back.

00:13:10.720 --> 00:13:12.080
Can't disturb his life.

00:14:04.759 --> 00:14:06.015
You haven't opened this package.

00:14:06.039 --> 00:14:07.039
Do you need my help?

00:14:08.759 --> 00:14:10.839
It's probably specialty
goods sent from the village.

00:14:13.080 --> 00:14:13.559
Dad,

00:14:13.720 --> 00:14:14.279
I'll take a shower first.

00:14:14.280 --> 00:14:15.360
Can you open it for me?

00:14:55.879 --> 00:14:56.879
Xiao Meng.

00:14:56.960 --> 00:14:58.080
Before we talk business,

00:14:58.360 --> 00:15:00.039
I need to apologize to you first.

00:15:00.399 --> 00:15:01.679
Remember a year ago

00:15:01.919 --> 00:15:03.000
the day you left?

00:15:03.039 --> 00:15:04.600
The IOU I gave you?

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:06.480
You didn't open it at the time.

00:15:06.799 --> 00:15:07.960
And I didn't force you.

00:15:08.879 --> 00:15:09.879
Over the years,

00:15:10.120 --> 00:15:11.600
whenever I think about it,

00:15:11.840 --> 00:15:13.120
I can't sleep.

00:15:13.879 --> 00:15:15.279
I was too selfish.

00:15:15.919 --> 00:15:18.039
But I think you can understand.

00:15:18.279 --> 00:15:20.159
At that time, the village
really had no money.

00:15:20.679 --> 00:15:21.679
But now it's better.

00:15:22.200 --> 00:15:24.039
More and more tourists are coming.

00:15:24.159 --> 00:15:25.440
The village's seafood products

00:15:25.559 --> 00:15:26.919
are directly sold overseas now.

00:15:27.399 --> 00:15:29.360
We can finally repay this money.

00:15:29.559 --> 00:15:31.159
No matter how old a person is,

00:15:31.600 --> 00:15:32.879
they have some bad habits.

00:15:33.240 --> 00:15:34.240
I don't have many.

00:15:34.519 --> 00:15:35.759
Just a bit shy.

00:15:36.639 --> 00:15:38.360
Can you help me get in touch with Yoki?

00:15:39.039 --> 00:15:40.279
Help me return it to him.

00:15:40.720 --> 00:15:43.639
The password is 101010.

00:15:44.720 --> 00:15:45.440
Oh, right.

00:15:45.720 --> 00:15:47.279
Two young people came to the village.

00:15:47.759 --> 00:15:49.879
They said they're your
junior high school classmates.

00:15:49.960 --> 00:15:50.919
Five days later,

00:15:50.920 --> 00:15:52.440
they want to hold their wedding here.

00:15:52.960 --> 00:15:55.000
I'm not sure if the package is fast or not,

00:15:55.480 --> 00:15:57.120
or if you end up getting it or not.

00:15:58.600 --> 00:15:59.120
Oh, right.

00:15:59.559 --> 00:16:01.039
They're two young men.

00:16:02.120 --> 00:16:03.879
We also didn't dare ask too much.

00:16:05.120 --> 00:16:06.279
Brother Yang Meng

00:16:06.559 --> 00:16:08.320
and Brother Yoki, hello.

00:16:09.000 --> 00:16:10.840
Hope your friendship lasts forever.

00:16:11.279 --> 00:16:11.840
This blessing

00:16:11.841 --> 00:16:13.799
were taught to me by Mom and Dad.

00:16:22.431 --> 00:16:24.872
(Greetings and updates from Xiao Hao
hoping Yang Meng comes back soon to Lanwan)

00:16:31.036 --> 00:16:33.243
[TN: Messy handwriting with more miscelaneous updates.]

00:16:37.319 --> 00:16:39.125
[TN: Auntie Liu sending auntie-style wishes]

00:17:10.512 --> 00:17:12.479
[Close up of the IOU]

00:18:08.400 --> 00:18:09.759
I was originally

00:18:10.000 --> 00:18:12.440
planning to tell you the
good news when you landed.

00:18:12.920 --> 00:18:14.400
But I just couldn't wait.

00:18:14.759 --> 00:18:15.480
My producer

00:18:15.481 --> 00:18:17.358
wants to invite you to play the

00:18:17.359 --> 00:18:19.440
male lead Ennis in the film.

00:18:19.799 --> 00:18:22.039
The other actor you'll surely like.

00:18:22.279 --> 00:18:24.119
His name is Jack Travis.

00:18:24.359 --> 00:18:25.759
Jack Travis!

00:18:26.440 --> 00:18:27.440
Lei.

00:18:27.640 --> 00:18:28.840
Let's meet and talk in detail.

00:18:42.240 --> 00:18:43.775
This is something I made with my own hands.

00:18:43.799 --> 00:18:44.799
Don't break it.

00:19:34.559 --> 00:19:36.559
Are you traveling
domestically or internationally?

00:23:28.160 --> 00:23:29.160
Buddy.

00:23:33.240 --> 00:23:34.240
Buddy.

00:24:46.039 --> 00:24:47.039
I thought

00:24:48.759 --> 00:24:49.759
you weren't coming.

00:24:52.240 --> 00:24:53.240
Your name is Yoki,

00:24:54.359 --> 00:24:55.440
not "I thought."

00:25:14.000 --> 00:25:15.279
Bought you a new one.

00:25:16.279 --> 00:25:17.440
Yours is too old.

00:25:54.920 --> 00:25:55.920
Then we're

00:25:56.887 --> 00:25:57.880
still going?

00:26:00.240 --> 00:26:01.240
What's the rush?

00:26:02.799 --> 00:26:03.799
It's been a year.

00:26:05.319 --> 00:26:06.319
Only a year.

00:26:08.400 --> 00:26:09.160
Do you know how this year

00:26:09.161 --> 00:26:10.279
has been for me?

00:27:17.880 --> 00:27:19.119
Did I draw it poorly?

00:27:20.799 --> 00:27:22.480
Pretty good, looks like you.

00:27:26.519 --> 00:27:27.680
After attending the wedding,

00:27:30.240 --> 00:27:31.359
are you still going back?

00:27:32.920 --> 00:27:33.920
Listen carefully.

00:27:36.720 --> 00:27:37.880
I know I'm pretty good. [TN:
Sounds like "listen carefully"]

00:27:38.319 --> 00:27:39.439
You don't need to praise me.

00:27:40.000 --> 00:27:41.920
I said listen carefully.

00:27:42.519 --> 00:27:43.920
Starting today,

00:27:44.559 --> 00:27:45.960
wherever you go,

00:27:46.759 --> 00:27:49.359
I'll go too.

00:27:54.920 --> 00:27:56.080
I just came back from Turkey.

00:27:56.119 --> 00:27:57.119
Really beautiful.

00:27:57.359 --> 00:27:58.480
Later I'll go to Thailand,

00:27:58.640 --> 00:27:59.999
Singapore, Indonesia.

00:28:00.000 --> 00:28:01.480
Wherever you go, I'll go.

00:29:06.005 --> 00:29:08.359
"Lanwan's Lonely Mountaintop Cafe invites you to bear witness to our happiness."

00:29:08.759 --> 00:29:10.919
Just having something to
eat and drink is enough, sis.

00:29:11.599 --> 00:29:12.599
Let me do it.

00:29:16.480 --> 00:29:17.480
Xiao Mei.

00:29:17.599 --> 00:29:19.358
Which one here is the groom?

00:29:19.359 --> 00:29:20.359
Which one is the bride?

00:29:20.759 --> 00:29:21.559
Or two brides?

00:29:21.559 --> 00:29:22.559
Two grooms?

00:29:23.039 --> 00:29:24.039
Confused.

00:29:24.119 --> 00:29:25.279
You know, Granny Tong,

00:29:25.839 --> 00:29:27.400
they're just two young people.

00:29:28.160 --> 00:29:29.359
Two young people?

00:29:30.079 --> 00:29:31.359
I don't get it, I just don't get it.

00:29:33.419 --> 00:29:34.400
The wind is so strong.

00:29:34.839 --> 00:29:36.200
It won't rain later, will it?

00:29:37.160 --> 00:29:38.039
I don't know if Brother Meng

00:29:38.040 --> 00:29:39.240
and Yoki are still coming.

00:29:42.680 --> 00:29:44.280
Hurry, hurry, we're running out of time.

00:29:52.119 --> 00:29:53.799
What kind of route did you find, bro?

00:29:59.400 --> 00:30:00.400
What's going on?

00:30:00.880 --> 00:30:02.000
Seems like the battery died.

00:30:07.832 --> 00:30:09.312
Why does this rain keep
starting and stopping?

00:30:09.960 --> 00:30:11.280
Summer weather is just like this.

00:30:11.799 --> 00:30:12.799
Let's not ride anymore.

00:30:13.839 --> 00:30:14.839
Forget the bag?

00:30:15.039 --> 00:30:16.439
With you, what do I need a bag for?

00:30:17.440 --> 00:30:18.880
Let's go, we're running out of time.

00:30:21.680 --> 00:30:23.680
Stop kissing, we're
running out of time, hurry up.

00:30:38.400 --> 00:30:39.240
These two are outside

00:30:39.400 --> 00:30:40.976
and have been standing for over an hour.

00:30:41.000 --> 00:30:42.119
It's raining so heavily.

00:30:43.000 --> 00:30:44.319
Can this wedding still start?

00:30:45.000 --> 00:30:46.720
Brother Yoki said he'll definitely make it.

00:30:46.880 --> 00:30:48.240
But if he can't arrive before six,

00:30:48.720 --> 00:30:50.160
can't they wait a bit?

00:30:51.440 --> 00:30:52.519
Only ten minutes left.

00:30:53.559 --> 00:30:54.559
Definitely won't make it.

00:30:54.960 --> 00:30:55.960
But if it can't happen,

00:30:56.359 --> 00:30:57.839
wouldn't all the work be for nothing?

00:30:58.519 --> 00:31:00.159
If it can't happen, then it can't happen.

00:31:00.920 --> 00:31:01.880
Those two classmates of his

00:31:01.880 --> 00:31:02.799
are so lovey-dovey as if

00:31:02.800 --> 00:31:04.120
there's no one else in the world.

00:31:04.480 --> 00:31:05.480
If they had the heart,

00:31:05.920 --> 00:31:07.680
they would've contacted
each other long ago.

00:31:09.319 --> 00:31:10.959
Are they as lovey-dovey as the two of us?

00:31:12.000 --> 00:31:14.000
I've said what I like about you.

00:31:15.400 --> 00:31:16.400
Alright.

00:31:25.880 --> 00:31:27.360
If I knew it was going to rain today,

00:31:27.519 --> 00:31:28.839
I wouldn't have worn white shoes.

00:31:29.480 --> 00:31:30.160
Looks like this rain

00:31:30.279 --> 00:31:31.680
shows no sign of stopping.

00:31:32.720 --> 00:31:33.720
Seems like

00:31:33.920 --> 00:31:34.720
that package

00:31:34.721 --> 00:31:35.841
probably hadn't arrived yet.

00:31:35.920 --> 00:31:36.920
Or it got lost.

00:31:37.640 --> 00:31:39.921
There probably isn't a
password inside the letter, right?

00:31:41.960 --> 00:31:42.359
Oh no.

00:31:42.599 --> 00:31:43.039
I need to

00:31:43.200 --> 00:31:44.240
call the bank quickly!

00:31:44.920 --> 00:31:45.640
Contact me if there's anything.

00:31:45.920 --> 00:31:47.119
Oh no, this is bad!

00:31:50.799 --> 00:31:51.400
Tell me,

00:31:51.640 --> 00:31:52.800
where did these two go again?

00:31:53.119 --> 00:31:54.719
Appearing and disappearing mysteriously.

00:31:55.039 --> 00:31:56.039
Never mind.

00:31:56.240 --> 00:31:57.279
Start on time.

00:31:58.279 --> 00:31:59.279
Wrap up when it's time.

00:32:01.720 --> 00:32:03.359
Five more minutes.

00:32:03.920 --> 00:32:05.039
Two minutes.

00:32:06.559 --> 00:32:07.559
Only one minute left.

00:32:10.200 --> 00:32:11.359
They're here.

00:32:27.759 --> 00:32:28.359
Bro.

00:32:28.480 --> 00:32:29.480
Classmate!

00:32:29.481 --> 00:32:31.079
Why are you two still so lovey-dovey?

00:32:31.400 --> 00:32:32.519
Exactly, exactly.